
Description:

Adds support for the Sieve 'processcalendar' action, which supersedes
the Cyrus-specific 'processimip' action.  See draft-ietf-extra-processimip.


Config changes:

The 'sieve_extensions' option SHOULD use the 'processcalendar' value
instead of 'vnd.cyrus.imip', but both will be accepted.


Upgrade instructions:

None, as the Cyrus Sieve engine will continue to process existing
bytecode containing the 'processimip' action.

New/updated scripts SHOULD use 'processcalendar' in lieu of
'processimip', but the Sieve parser/compiler will automatically
translate the latter into the former.
